text: The Canberra Raiders are an Australian professional rugby league team. The team is based in the nation's capital city of Canberra, Australian Capital Territory. They were founded in 1981. They currently play in the National Rugby League competition. They have won three premierships, most recently in 1994. ==Other websites== * Category:National Rugby League Category:Organisations based in Canberra Category:1981 establishments in Australia Category:Sport in Canberra
